<section class="origin" id="origin">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="origin-grid">
      <div class="origin-image" data-animate="slide-left">
        <img src="/brothers.png" alt="James and Brendan, founders of Brothers Automate" width="280" height="280" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      </div>
      <div class="origin-content" data-animate="slide-right">
        <h2>Built by Operators, for Operators</h2>
        <p>We ran a service business for 5 years. We lived it. The 14-hour days, the manual grind, the leads slipping through cracks while you're busy doing the actual work.</p>
        <p>
          We built AI systems to handle that work automatically, and do it better than a human could. AI can't close your deals or deliver your service, but it can follow up with your leads, create your ads, and keep your pipeline moving.
        </p>
        <p>
          Agencies charge $10K/month for this work. Hiring someone costs the same or more. Learning it yourself takes hundreds of hours you don't have.
        </p>
        <p class="origin-cta">
          <strong>We build the systems so you don't have to pay agency prices or sacrifice your time.</strong>
        </p>
        <div class="origin-button">
          <a
            href="#"
            class="btn btn-primary"
            data-cal-link="james-pinder-simpleflo/free-quiz-audit-automation-brothers"
            data-cal-namespace="free-quiz-audit-automation-brothers"
            data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view","useSlotsViewOnSmallScreen":"true"}'
          >Talk to the Brothers</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .origin {
    background: var(--bg-surface-alt);
  }

  .origin-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .origin-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-3xl);
    }
  }

  .origin-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .origin-image img {
    width: 250px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .origin-image img {
      width: 280px;
    }
  }

  .origin-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .origin-content p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .origin-cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .origin-cta strong {
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
  }

  .origin-button {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
